Package InfrastructureManager.ModuleManagement

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImmutablePlatformModule
    Interface for the different modules to implement to appear as read-only immutable objects
    PlatformInput
    Interface that defines an input for the Edge Diagnostics Platform.
    PlatformOutput
    Interface that defines an output for the Edge Diagnostics Platform.
    RunnerOperation
    Functional interface to represent an operation to be passed to a Runner to perform inside a loop.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Connection
    Represents a Connection inside a Module.
    ModuleConnector
    Class that is in charge of connecting PlatformModule objects, based on connection raw data.
    ModuleDebugInput
    Built in input in all platform modules.
    ModuleFactory
    Factory for PlatformModule objects.
    ModuleManager
    Class that allows to create, connect and manipulate the modules of the platform.
    PlatformModule
    Abstract class to represent a platform module.
    Runner
    Class implementing the Runnable interface to be run in different threads.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ModuleFactory.ModuleType
    Enum representing the valid module types that the platform supports.
    PlatformModule.ModuleState
    Enum to represent the state of a module.
